evaluation.response:
I totally get it; it can be really weird when your imagination starts playing tricks on you like that. Keep in mind that tons of people experience similar things.&#x20;

Maybe try listening more closely to the sound. Is it coming from a specific place or direction? Maybe it’s just the sound of the wind going down something - like a pipe or a wire. It can create a lot of different sounds.

Or, maybe your brain is just playing a trick on you. That happens too. I guess it is kind of natural, isn’t it? Even to have nightmares! Again: YOU ARE NOT ALONE WITH THESE THOUGHTS. More to come.&#x20;
